---
title: Soy-Ginger Glazed Salmon with Garlicky Stir-Fried Greens
description: A little sweet, a little savoury, and a whole lot of delicious! This delicate salmon dish is beautifully tender and packed with umami-rich flavour, paired with garlicky stir-fried greens for the perfect balance. Light, tasty, and totally satisfying - you’re in for a real treat tonight!

